Reduce - items have less burden, incriments of 2% up to a 50% reduction

Reuse - Processes and phyiscal stations for storage, cleaning, refilling

Recycle - Mainly upcycle of waste from world. Some onboard recycling.

Philosophy Leave a positive trace
Increased biodiversity
Reduce historic pollution
Recover and recycle waste 

Mechanic ideas:

Skills to learn for benefit : life cycle analysis

Some % of burden can only be processed with a 'long rest' style mechanic, that has other costs, or requires physical action (turn encoder?)
Some % or types of burden cannot be processed at sea: toxic, radioactive, pathogenic - stored as Bad Pearls = encased in glass spheres

Reed beds, algae, many levels and layers of filtration.
